      <tr><td>Inlet valve</td><td>$240 – $380</td><td>F6 code</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door latch + switch</td><td>$200 – $320</td><td>5-8 year wear</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door gasket</td><td>$220 – $380</td><td>6-8 year service</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Heating element</td><td>$260 – $420</td><td>F3 code / Sani Rinse</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Sensor Cycle sensor</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>Adaptive-cycle drift</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Rinse-aid dispenser service</td><td>$140 – $220</td><td>Clog / mechanism</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Spray arm replacement</td><td>$140 – $240</td><td>Upper or lower</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Vent flap mechanism</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>Dry-cycle fault</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Control board</td><td>$380 – $580</td><td>F-code diagnostic</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Membrane switch</td><td>$240 – $360</td><td>Panel fault</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Circulation pump</td><td>$420 – $620</td><td>8-plus-year service</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/price-list/dishwasher-repair-cost/">dishwasher repair cost guide</a> · <a href="/brands/kitchenaid-dishwasher-repair/">KitchenAid</a> · <a href="/brands/maytag-dishwasher-repair/">Maytag</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Service areas — where our Whirlpool calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>San Fernando Valley</h4><p>Sherman Oaks · Van Nuys · Northridge · Woodland Hills · <a href="/encino/">Encino</a></p></div>
      <div><h4>San Gabriel Valley</h4><p><a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · Alhambra · Monterey Park · Arcadia</p></div>
